        "step": "Bloom the gelatin by sprinkling {{gelatin}} over {{water}} and letting it stand for 5 minutes.",
        "variables": {
          "gelatin": { "quantity_per_serving": 3, "unit": "grams" },
          "water": { "quantity_per_serving": 15, "unit": "ml" }
        }
      },
      {
        "step": "In a saucepan, combine cream, milk, and sugar."
      },
      {
